data.rationale:
This module is specific to the Gnu C Compiler. I forsee several
    other modules filling this namespace in the future, especially with
    this one as a building-block.

    There are several efforts underway to extract useful information
    from GCC to use in interfacing with other languages -- specifically
    see the .NET projects. Also see gccxml.org for another attempt at
    making this GCC data accessible in an especially portable way.
